        {
            "title": "南韓KOSPI指數在晶片股反彈和伊朗和平希望推動下逼近歷史高點",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/cnuI5Tv_0wsbw9g616LjUQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/asian_3_M_1440047966.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 南韓KOSPI指數週三大幅上漲,再次逼近歷史高點,記憶體晶片股的漲勢以及美伊外交關係改善的樂觀情緒提振了風險偏好。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">截至格林威治標準時間01:29,基準指數攀升3.6%至6,183.21點,徘徊在2月觸及的6,347.4點歷史高點下方。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資者紛紛湧入半導體龍頭股,預期人工智慧將推動強勁需求。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隔夜美股強勁收盤,標普500指數上漲約1.2%,收盤時僅略低於歷史高點,而納斯達克指數飆升近2%。此次反彈由科技股、油價回落以及美伊會談可能恢復的樂觀情緒推動。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-03fe2f78-dd53-3b78-a2fc-2fb93d0b7ad5-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">三星電子(KS:005930)股價週三延續大幅漲勢,而SK海力士(KS:000660)股價則飆升至新的歷史高點。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">更廣泛的市場情緒也受到中東緊張局勢緩和的謹慎樂觀情緒支撐。美國總統唐納德·川普本週早些時候表示,與伊朗的會談可能正在取得進展,儘管風險仍然高企,但這提升了外交突破的希望。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">油價降溫和美國生產者通脹數據走軟進一步支撐了股市,強化了全球價格壓力可能正在緩解的預期。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%93kospi%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8%E5%9C%A8%E6%99%B6%E7%89%87%E8%82%A1%E5%8F%8D%E5%BD%88%E5%92%8C%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E5%92%8C%E5%B9%B3%E5%B8%8C%E6%9C%9B%E6%8E%A8%E5%8B%95%E4%B8%8B%E9%80%BC%E8%BF%91%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2%E9%AB%98%E9%BB%9E-023518049.html",
